3. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper deals with network protocols and their performance, which is a topic closely related to networking and internet architecture. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper deals with control of distributed systems, which falls under the scope of systems and control.
